  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Ugh, it's 7 o'clock.",
      "zh": "唉，現在七點了。",
      "ja": "うう、もう7時だ。",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I turn off my alarm so early, but okay, okay, I'm awake.",
      "zh": "我這麼早就關掉鬧鐘，好吧，好吧，我醒了。",
      "ja": "こんなに早くアラームを止めたけど、よしよし、起きたよ。",
      "time": "00:00:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This is my new apartment, sunrise apartment, unit 402.",
      "zh": "這是我的新公寓，日出公寓，402號單元。",
      "ja": "ここが私の新しいアパート、サンライズアパートメントの402号室。",
      "time": "00:00:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My first morning here.",
      "zh": "我在這裡的第一個早晨。",
      "ja": "ここでの最初の朝。",
      "time": "00:00:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's do this.",
      "zh": "開始吧。",
      "ja": "さあ、やろう。",
      "time": "00:00:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Time to get up.",
      "zh": "該起床了。",
      "ja": "起きる時間だ。",
      "time": "00:00:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I sit on my bed, my feet touch the floor, mmm, it's cold.",
      "zh": "我坐在床上，腳碰到地板，嗯，好冷。",
      "ja": "ベッドに座って足が床に触れる、うーん、冷たい。",
      "time": "00:00:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I need slippers.",
      "zh": "我需要拖鞋。",
      "ja": "スリッパが必要だ。",
      "time": "00:00:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Where are my slippers?",
      "zh": "我的拖鞋在哪裡？",
      "ja": "スリッパはどこ？",
      "time": "00:00:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh well, I'm too sleepy to look for them right now.",
      "zh": "算了，我現在太睏了，不想找。",
      "ja": "まあいいや、今は眠すぎて探せない。",
      "time": "00:00:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I walk to my window, I pull open the curtains, and wow, so much sunshine.",
      "zh": "我走到窗邊，拉開窗簾，哇，好多陽光。",
      "ja": "窓まで歩いてカーテンを開けると、わあ、たくさんの日差し。",
      "time": "00:00:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I love this fig window.",
      "zh": "我喜歡這扇大窗戶。",
      "ja": "この大きな窓が大好き。",
      "time": "00:00:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "My old apartment was so dark.",
      "zh": "我以前的公寓很暗。",
      "ja": "前のアパートはとても暗かった。",
      "time": "00:00:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is much better.",
      "zh": "這裡好多了。",
      "ja": "ここはずっといい。",
      "time": "00:01:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good morning world.",
      "zh": "早安，世界。",
      "ja": "おはよう、世界。",
      "time": "00:01:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay, let's make my bed.",
      "zh": "好，來整理床鋪。",
      "ja": "よし、ベッドを整えよう。",
      "time": "00:01:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I shake my blanket one, two, three.",
      "zh": "我抖抖毯子，一、二、三。",
      "ja": "毛布を振って、一、二、三。",
      "time": "00:01:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I put my pillow nice and straight.",
      "zh": "我把枕頭擺好擺正。",
      "ja": "枕をきれいにまっすぐ置く。",
      "time": "00:01:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "There, my bed looks good.",
      "zh": "好了，我的床看起來很棒。",
      "ja": "はい、ベッドがきれいになった。",
      "time": "00:01:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm such a good adult.",
      "zh": "我真是個好成年人。",
      "ja": "私は立派な大人だな。",
      "time": "00:01:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Mom would be so proud.",
      "zh": "媽媽一定會很驕傲。",
      "ja": "お母さんはきっと誇りに思うだろう。",
      "time": "00:01:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I look in the mirror.",
      "zh": "我看著鏡子。",
      "ja": "鏡を見た。",
      "time": "00:01:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh no, my hair is crazy.",
      "zh": "糟糕，我的頭髮亂了。",
      "ja": "ああ、髪がぐちゃぐちゃだ。",
      "time": "00:01:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's everywhere.",
      "zh": "到處都是。",
      "ja": "どこもかしこも。",
      "time": "00:01:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I need to tie it back.",
      "zh": "我需要把它綁起來。",
      "ja": "髪を結ばないと。",
      "time": "00:01:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Where's my hair tie?",
      "zh": "我的髮圈在哪裡？",
      "ja": "ヘアゴムはどこ？",
      "time": "00:01:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I bite it with my teeth, pull my hair back, and done.",
      "zh": "我用牙齒咬著髮圈，拉起頭髮，完成了。",
      "ja": "歯でヘアゴムを咥えて髪を結んだ、できた。",
      "time": "00:01:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Much better.",
      "zh": "好多了。",
      "ja": "ずっといい。",
      "time": "00:01:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Now I wash my face.",
      "zh": "現在我要洗臉。",
      "ja": "今から顔を洗う。",
      "time": "00:01:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The water is so cold, splash, splash, burr, but it wakes me up.",
      "zh": "水好冷，噗通噗通，哇，但它讓我清醒。",
      "ja": "水が冷たい、バシャバシャ、ぶるっ、でも目が覚める。",
      "time": "00:01:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I feel fresh now.",
      "zh": "我現在感覺很清新。",
      "ja": "今はさっぱりした気分。",
      "time": "00:02:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay, I'm ready for the day.",
      "zh": "好，我準備好迎接一天了。",
      "ja": "よし、一日の準備ができた。",
      "time": "00:02:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, almost ready.",
      "zh": "嗯，差不多準備好了。",
      "ja": "まあ、ほぼ準備完了。",
      "time": "00:02:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Time to brush my teeth.",
      "zh": "該刷牙了。",
      "ja": "歯を磨く時間だ。",
      "time": "00:02:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I turn on my electric toothbrush.",
      "zh": "我打開電動牙刷。",
      "ja": "電動歯ブラシのスイッチを入れる。",
      "time": "00:02:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Buzz, buzz, buzz.",
      "zh": "嗡嗡嗡。",
      "ja": "ブーン、ブーン、ブーン。",
      "time": "00:02:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So many bubbles.",
      "zh": "好多泡泡。",
      "ja": "泡がたくさん。",
      "time": "00:02:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I look funny in the mirror.",
      "zh": "我在鏡子裡看起來很滑稽。",
      "ja": "鏡の中の自分が面白い顔をしている。",
      "time": "00:02:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I smile at myself.",
      "zh": "我對自己微笑。",
      "ja": "自分に笑いかける。",
      "time": "00:02:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Nice to meet you, Ashley, from Unit 402.",
      "zh": "很高興認識你，來自402號單元的Ashley。",
      "ja": "はじめまして、402号室のアシュリーです。",
      "time": "00:02:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Now my face cream.",
      "zh": "現在擦臉霜。",
      "ja": "次はフェイスクリーム。",
      "time": "00:02:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I put some on my fingers.",
      "zh": "我把一些塗在手指上。",
      "ja": "指に少し取る。",
      "time": "00:02:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Pat, pat, pat on my cheeks.",
      "zh": "輕拍我的臉頰。",
      "ja": "ほっぺたにトントンと塗る。",
      "time": "00:02:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Pat, pat on my forehead.",
      "zh": "輕拍我的額頭。",
      "ja": "おでこにもトントン。",
      "time": "00:02:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "My skin feels soft and nice.",
      "zh": "我的皮膚感覺柔軟又舒服。",
      "ja": "肌が柔らかくて気持ちいい。",
      "time": "00:02:54"
    },
    {
