      "text": "Okay, I look good.",
      "zh": "好了，我看起來不錯。",
      "ja": "よし、いい感じ。",
      "time": "00:02:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm ready.",
      "zh": "我準備好了。",
      "ja": "準備完了。",
      "time": "00:03:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What should I wear today?",
