      "time": "00:03:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The blue shirt or the yellow one?",
      "zh": "藍色襯衫還是黃色的？",
      "ja": "青いシャツか黄色いシャツか？",
      "time": "00:03:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hmm, I have class with Tom today.",
