    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe the blue one?",
      "zh": "也許穿藍色的？",
      "ja": "青い方かな？",
      "time": "00:03:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Or no, the yellow one is more fun.",
      "zh": "不，黃色的比較有趣。",
