      "text": "It's warm and soft.",
      "zh": "它又暖和又柔軟。",
      "ja": "暖かくて柔らかい。",
      "time": "00:03:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I love it.",
      "zh": "我喜歡它。",
